Package: cardim
Type: Package
Title: CARDIM-model tools for prediction
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Asier Ballesteros Domínguez
Maintainer: Methodoloy unit of Navarrabiomed <metodologia.navarrabiomed@navarra.es>
Description: This package is a set of tools that allow the user to properly predict
    the cardiovascular risk of new patients using the CARDIM-model definition.
    Even more it have tools to obtain the external validation results. 
    The discrimination is calculated witht he Harrell's c-index and 
    the calibration with calibration plots.
